name: CaptainKitten's Awesome Website
tagline: CaptainKitten, the cool cat of coding
body:
# CaptainKitten


An English freelance programmer that loves Persian cats, playing Minecraft, Drinking Tea and generally mucking about

I am a founder of [KittenKoding](kittenkoding.github.io) I love to program with my mate [Bryce](mrmappyinof.github.io)

### Want to add to a KittenKoding Project?

Fork one of my programs and make your changes and send a pull request, if merged 
we will invite you to KittenKoding.
